dia.vn\/cac-hinh-thuc-quang-cao-tren-zalo-ads.html\/#1_Quang_cao_Zalo_Official_Account\" title=\"1. Qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o Zalo Official Account\">1. Qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o Zalo Official Account<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-4'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/cac-hinh-thuc-quang-cao-tren-zalo-ads.html\/#2_Quang_cao_website\" title=\"2.\u00a0Qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o website\">2.\u00a0Qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o website<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-4'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/cac-hinh-thuc-quang-cao-tren-zalo-ads.html\/#3_Quang_cao_video\" title=\"3. Qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o video\">3. Qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o video<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-4'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/cac-hinh-thuc-quang-cao-tren-zalo-ads.html\/#4_Quang_cao_bai_viet\" title=\"4.\u00a0Qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft\">4.\u00a0Qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-4'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/cac-hinh-thuc-quang-cao-tren-zalo-ads.html\/#5_Quang_cao_san_pham\" title=\"5. Qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m\">5. Qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-4'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-6\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/cac-hinh-thuc-quang-cao-tren-zalo-ads.html\/#6_Quang_cao_Form\" title=\"6. Qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o Form\">6. Qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o Form<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-4'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-7\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/cac-hinh-thuc-quang-cao-tren-zalo-ads.html\/#7_Quang_cao_tin_dang\" title=\"7. Qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o tin \u0111\u0103ng\">7. Qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o tin \u0111\u0103ng<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-4'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-8\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/cac-hinh-thuc-quang-cao-tren-zalo-ads.html\/#8_Quang_cao_tin_nhan\" title=\"8. Qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o tin nh\u1eafn\">8. Qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o tin nh\u1eafn<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<p>Th\u00f4ng qua 8 h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o kh\u00e1c nhau, Zalo Ads c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 nh\u00e0 nh\u00e0 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o (ch\u1ee7 doanh nghi\u1ec7p, ch\u1ee7 c\u1eeda h\u00e0ng,\u2026) l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi t\u1eebng m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch kh\u00e1c nhau nh\u01b0: x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u, thu h\u00fat kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng, t\u0103ng doanh thu,\u2026<\/p>\n<h4><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"1_Quang_cao_Zalo_Official_Account\"><\/span><strong>1. Qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o Zalo Official Account<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h4>\n<figure id=\"attachment_15334\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-15334\" style=\"width: 388px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-15334 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1-7.png\" alt=\"Quang-cao-zalo-official-account\" width=\"388\" height=\"774\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1-7.png 388w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1-7-150x300.png 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 388px) 100vw, 388px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-15334\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o Zalo Official Account<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o t\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng quan t\u00e2m trang Zalo Official Account c\u1ee7a doanh nghi\u1ec7p, c\u1eeda h\u00e0ng.<\/p>\n<p>V\u1edbi qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o Zalo Official Account, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>T\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3t quan t\u00e2m cho t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n Official Account<\/li>\n<li>Sau \u0111\u00f3, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn l\u1ea1i nh\u00f3m kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng n\u00e0y d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng v\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c t\u00ednh n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Zalo Official Account.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>\u0110i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c lo\u1ea1i qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o n\u00e0y b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n\u00a0<strong>t\u1ea1o Zalo Official Account<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>H\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c t\u00ednh ph\u00ed:\u00a0<strong>CPC<\/strong><\/p>\n<h4><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"2_Quang_cao_website\"><\/span><strong>2.\u00a0<\/strong><strong>Qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o website<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h4>\n<figure id=\"attachment_15333\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-15333\" style=\"width: 388px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-15333 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/3-2.png\" alt=\"quang-cao-website\" width=\"388\" height=\"774\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/3-2.png 388w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/3-2-150x300.png 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 388px) 100vw, 388px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-15333\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o website<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o website h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 nh\u00e0 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u website c\u1ee7a doanh nghi\u1ec7p\/c\u1eeda h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng Zalo.<\/p>\n<p>V\u1edbi qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o website, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Chuy\u1ec3n m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ebfn trang li\u00ean k\u1ebft c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ec3 mua h\u00e0ng ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i th\u00f4ng tin t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n.<\/li>\n<li>T\u0103ng s\u1ed1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111i t\u1edbi \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng tr\u00ean thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb di \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>\u0110i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n t\u1ea1o lo\u1ea1i qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o n\u00e0y b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n c\u00f3\u00a0<strong>Zalo Official Account<\/strong>\u00a0v\u00e0\u00a0<strong>trang website\u00a0<\/strong>c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.<\/p>\n<p>H\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c t\u00ednh ph\u00ed:\u00a0<strong>CPC<\/strong><\/p>\n<h4><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"3_Quang_cao_video\"><\/span><strong>3. Qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o video<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h4>\n<p>\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c gi\u00fap qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi mua h\u00e0ng m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch tr\u1ef1c quan, sinh \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o h\u01a1n.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_15335\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-15335\" style=\"width: 388px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-15335 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/33-1.png\" alt=\"quang-cao-video\" width=\"388\" height=\"774\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/33-1.png 388w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/33-1-150x300.png 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 388px) 100vw, 388px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-15335\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o video<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>V\u1edbi qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o video, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>T\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9 nh\u1eadn di\u1ec7n th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a doanh nghi\u1ec7p.<\/li>\n<li>Chuy\u1ec3n m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ebfn trang li\u00ean k\u1ebft c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ec3 mua h\u00e0ng ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i th\u00f4ng tin t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>\u0110i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n t\u1ea1o lo\u1ea1i qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o n\u00e0y b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n c\u00f3\u00a0<strong>video\u00a0<\/strong>v\u00e0\u00a0<strong>trang website<\/strong>\u00a0c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.<\/p>\n<p>H\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c t\u00ednh ph\u00ed:\u00a0<strong>CPV, CPM<\/strong><\/p>\n<h4><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"4_Quang_cao_bai_viet\"><\/span><strong>4.<\/strong>\u00a0<strong>Qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h4>\n<p>Qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft l\u00e0 h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o n\u1ed9i dung b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1edfi t\u1ea1o tr\u00ean Zalo Official Account c\u1ee7a doanh nghi\u1ec7p ho\u1eb7c c\u1eeda h\u00e0ng tr\u00ean Zalo.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_15336\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-15336\" style=\"width: 388px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-15336 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/7-1.png\" alt=\"quang-cao-bai-viet\" width=\"388\" height=\"774\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/7-1.png 388w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/7-1-150x300.png 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 388px) 100vw, 388px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-15336\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>V\u1edbi qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>D\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng kh\u1edfi t\u1ea1o, t\u00edch h\u1ee3p s\u1eb5n trong h\u1ec7 sinh th\u00e1i c\u1ee7a Zalo Official Account<\/li>\n<li>Gia t\u0103ng nh\u1eadn bi\u1ebft th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u v\u00e0 t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 mua h\u00e0ng.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>\u0110i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n t\u1ea1o lo\u1ea1i qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o n\u00e0y b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n c\u00f3\u00a0<strong>Zalo Official Account<\/strong>\u00a0v\u00e0\u00a0<strong>b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft<\/strong>\u00a0trong Zalo Official Account.<\/p>\n<p>H\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c t\u00ednh ph\u00ed:\u00a0<strong>CPC<\/strong><\/p>\n<h4><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"5_Quang_cao_san_pham\"><\/span><strong>5. Qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h4>\n<p>Qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m l\u00e0 h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c t\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3t nh\u1ea5n v\u00e0o trang th\u00f4ng tin s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_15337\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-15337\" style=\"width: 388px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-15337 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/5-4.png\" alt=\"quang-cao-san-pham\" width=\"388\" height=\"774\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/5-4.png 388w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/5-4-150x300.png 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 388px) 100vw, 388px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-15337\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>V\u1edbi qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Qu\u1ea3ng b\u00e1 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u1ee7a c\u1eeda h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ebfn kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng<\/li>\n<li>T\u0103ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1ed1t \u0111\u01a1n h\u00e0ng ngay tr\u00ean ch\u00ednh Zalo.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>\u0110i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n t\u1ea1o lo\u1ea1i qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o n\u00e0y b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n c\u00f3\u00a0<strong>Zalo Official Account<\/strong>\u00a0v\u00e0\u00a0<strong>s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m<\/strong>\u00a0\u0111\u0103ng tr\u00ean Zalo Official Account (\u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c duy\u1ec7t).<\/p>\n<p>H\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c t\u00ednh ph\u00ed:\u00a0<strong>CPC, L\u01b0\u1ee3t li\u00ean h\u1ec7<\/strong><\/p>\n<h4><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"6_Quang_cao_Form\"><\/span><strong>6. Qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o Form<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h4>\n<figure id=\"attachment_15338\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-15338\" style=\"width: 481px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-15338 size-full\" style=\"color: #555555; font-size: 14.4px;\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/11.png\" alt=\"quang-cao-form\" width=\"481\" height=\"960\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/11.png 481w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/11-150x300.png 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 481px) 100vw, 481px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-15338\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o Form<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>H\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o nh\u1eb1m m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch thu th\u1eadp th\u00f4ng tin kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng gi\u00fap c\u1eeda h\u00e0ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c danh s\u00e1ch kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c Form ch\u1ec9 \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng cho m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ng\u00e0nh h\u00e0ng. Nh\u00e0 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o vui l\u00f2ng ki\u1ec3m tra k\u1ef9 th\u00f4ng tin.<\/p>\n<p>V\u1edbi qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o form, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>T\u1ed1i \u01b0u t\u1ec9 l\u1ec7 chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed5i kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o<\/li>\n<li>Cho ph\u00e9p kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng cung c\u1ea5p th\u00f4ng tin li\u00ean h\u1ec7 theo h\u1ecd t\u00ean, s\u1ed1 \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i, email, \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ec9\u2026.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>\u0110i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n t\u1ea1o lo\u1ea1i qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o n\u00e0y b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n c\u00f3\u00a0<strong>Zalo Official Account<\/strong> v\u00e0 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m\/d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 ph\u1ea3i thu\u1ed9c ng\u00e0nh h\u00e0ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3.<\/p>\n<p>H\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c t\u00ednh ph\u00ed:\u00a0<strong>CPC<\/strong><\/p>\n<h4><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"7_Quang_cao_tin_dang\"><\/span><strong>7. Qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o tin \u0111\u0103ng<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h4>\n<p>Qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o tin \u0111\u0103ng (Listing Ads) tr\u00ean Zalo Ads h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 nh\u00e0 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o ng\u00e0nh B\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n v\u00e0 Xe qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb tin \u0111\u0103ng t\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng h\u01a1n sau khi \u0111\u0103ng tin b\u00e1n h\u00e0ng tr\u00ean Zalo Home &amp; Car.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-15340 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/z3080635604850_d6e7fb1850468024e2e3896c4e568f99-700x665-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"700\" height=\"665\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/z3080635604850_d6e7fb1850468024e2e3896c4e568f99-700x665-1.jpg 700w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/z3080635604850_d6e7fb1850468024e2e3896c4e568f99-700x665-1-300x285.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>V\u1edbi qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o tin \u0111\u0103ng, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng Zalo kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 trang web b\u00e1n h\u00e0ng, ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c tin \u0111\u0103ng c\u1ea7n b\u00e1n l\u00ean Home &amp; Car sau \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ecdn ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng ch\u1ea1y qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o,<\/li>\n<li>Khi ng\u01b0\u1eddi mua nh\u1ea5n v\u00e0o qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o tin \u0111\u0103ng, h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng s\u1ebd m\u1edf ra th\u00f4ng tin chi ti\u1ebft v\u1ec1 tin \u0111\u0103ng gi\u00fap ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m,<\/li>\n<li>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi mua c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chat v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u00e1n ngay th\u00f4ng qua Zalo chat sau khi xem tin \u0111\u0103ng.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>\u0110i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n t\u1ea1o lo\u1ea1i qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o n\u00e0y b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n c\u00f3:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>\u0110\u0103ng th\u00f4ng tin s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m l\u00ean Zalo Home &amp; Car b\u1eb1ng t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n Zalo c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n<\/li>\n<li>Nh\u00e0 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o c\u1ea7n b\u1eadt ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9\u00a0<strong>\u201cCho ph\u00e9p ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u1ea1 nh\u1eafn tin\u201d\u00a0<\/strong>tr\u00ean Zalo\u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u0103ng tin tr\u00ean Home &amp; Car v\u00e0 ch\u1ea1y Qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o Tin \u0111\u0103ng.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"8_Quang_cao_tin_nhan\"><\/span><strong>8. Qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o tin nh\u1eafn<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h4>\n<p>Qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o tin nh\u1eafn (Message Ads) tr\u00ean Zalo Ads l\u00e0 h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 nh\u00e0 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng qua tin nh\u1eafn h\u1ed9p tho\u1ea1i tr\u00ean Zalo. Qua \u0111\u00f3, nh\u00e0 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thu th\u1eadp th\u00f4ng tin kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng, t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp 1:1, ho\u1eb7c ch\u1ed1t \u0111\u01a1n h\u00e0ng tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp ngay tr\u00ean Zalo.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_15341\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-15341\" style=\"width: 700px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-15341 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/message-ads-1-700x381-1.png\" alt=\"quang-cao-tin-nhan\" width=\"700\" height=\"381\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/message-ads-1-700x381-1.png 700w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/message-ads-1-700x381-1-300x163.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-15341\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Qu\u1ea3ng-c\u00e1o-tin-nh\u1eafn<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>V\u1edbi qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o tin nh\u1eafn, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Khi ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng nh\u1ea5n v\u00e0o qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o, h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng s\u1ebd m\u1edf ra h\u1ed9p tho\u1ea1i nhanh ch\u00f3ng v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp 1:1 v\u1edbi doanh nghi\u1ec7p.<\/li>\n<li>Nh\u00e0 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o\/doanh nghi\u1ec7p c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn l\u1ea1i nh\u00f3m kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng n\u00e0y trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai v\u1edbi b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft, ho\u1eb7c c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m m\u1edbi\/ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh khuy\u1ebfn m\u1ea1i m\u1edbi cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng.<\/li>\n<li>T\u0103ng t\u1ec9 l\u1ec7 chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed5i ra \u0111\u01a1n h\u00e0ng khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Chatbot \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>\u0110i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n t\u1ea1o lo\u1ea1i qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o n\u00e0y b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n c\u00f3\u00a0<strong>Zalo Official Account<\/strong> (\u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e1c th\u1ef1c) v\u00e0 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m\/d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 ph\u1ea3i thu\u1ed9c ng\u00e0nh h\u00e0ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3.<\/p>\n<p>H\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c t\u00ednh ph\u00ed:\u00a0<strong>CPC<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>\u0110\u1ecdc th\u00eam:<\/p>\n<p class=\"entry-title\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikimarketing.vn\/cach-su-dung-tu-dong-hoa-de-nang-cao.html\/\">C\u00e1ch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng h\u00f3a \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng cao (kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m h\u1ecfng) chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfp th\u1ecb c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n<\/a><\/p>\n<p class=\"entry-title\"><a href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/quang-cao-zalo-tep-khach-sdt.html\/\">T\u1ea1o qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o Zalo v\u1edbi t\u1ec7p kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng theo S\u0110T<\/a><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Th\u00f4ng qua 8 h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o kh\u00e1c nhau, Zalo Ads c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 nh\u00e0 nh\u00e0 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o (ch\u1ee7 doanh nghi\u1ec7p, ch\u1ee7 c\u1eeda h\u00e0ng,\u2026) l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o ph\